### Отримати всі компанії
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Companie
Accept: application/json

### Отримати компанію за ID
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Companie/{{companieId}}
Accept: application/json

### Створити нову компанію
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Companie
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Tech Solutions Ltd",
  "emailCompany": "info@techsolutions.com",
  "address": "вул. Шевченка, 123, Київ",
  "phone": "+380441234567",
  "activityTypeId": "{{activityTypeId}}"
}

### Оновити компанію
PUT https://localhost:7001/api/Companie/{{companieId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Tech Solutions Ukraine Ltd",
  "emailCompany": "contact@techsolutions.ua",
  "address": "вул. Хрещатик, 456, Київ",
  "phone": "+380449876543",
  "activityTypeId": "{{activityTypeId}}"
}

### Видалити компанію
DELETE https://localhost:7001/api/Companie/{{companieId}}
Accept: application/json

